## Registering your ENS name
Registering an ENS name is a three step process:
:::info Transaction details
```mermaid
%%{
  init: {
    'flowchart': {
      'curve': 'linear'
      } } }%%

graph LR;
A(Request to Register);
B(Wait 60 Seconds);
C(Register);

classDef active stroke-width:4px;
classDef inactive stroke-dasharray: 5 5;

A-->B-->C;
```

